acceptance_criteria: "pm graph slack reports earliest/latest start, total float, critical classification, and makespan over the order-bearing DAG with genuine cycles excluded; pm graph centrality reports exact Brandes betweenness, Wasserman-Faust closeness, undirected degree, and directed fan-in/fan-out ranked deterministically; pm graph articulation reports articulation points and bridges via iterative Tarjan low-link search; all three are exact on the bounded workspace, deterministic, cancellable, carry cost/truncation/cache metadata, honor --kind (centrality/articulation) and --limit/--summary bounds; CLI, MCP, contracts, completion, and docs stay in parity; exact 100/100/100/100 coverage"
